mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label:
Disco Elysium skill checks:
- Character gets to spend 12 points in total on 4 branches at the beginning of the game. (Adjust them however you want)
- They can spend up to 6 points in a branch and a minimum of 1 is required
- Skill checks are performed by rolling 2 dices. There is a total needed in order to pass the check (depending on the check difficulty)
- Rolling a 2 is always a failed check. Rolling a 12 is always a succeeded check (regardless of the total)
